  "text": "The very recent work of Jiang and Li [CITATION_1] presents an algorithm for solving the GTRS up to an additive error in the objective with high probability under the regularity condition. This algorithm relies on machinery developed by [CITATION_2] for solving the TRS and differs from previous algorithms in that it does not assume the ability to compute a simultaneously-diagonalizing basis or generalized eigenvalues. The running time of this algorithm isÕ",
